name: Alabama A & M University
ACCREDAGENCY: Southern Association of Colleges and Schools Commission on Colleges

lilgrant_international.Scholarship's Information: For out-of-state, first-time freshmen. Must be unconditionally admitted. Award based on a Composite Predictive Index (CPI) score calculated during admission. Renewable with a 2.80 GPA and completion of 30 credit hours per year.
